                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-24-off138 t18301209-24-cd139"></join>, 1 waistcoat, value 9s.; 1 silk handkerchief, value 1s. 6d.; 1 coat, value 6s.; 1 pin, value 6d.; 1 seal, value 6d,, and 1 key, value 1d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18301209-24-victim324" type="victimName">
                     Joseph 
                     Hill
